column4:
select u.nickname, fullname, about, email from forums_users
join users u on forums_users.id = u.id
where forum = $1 order by u.nickname limit $2
select id, title, message, votes, slug, created, forum, author from threads where forum = $1 and created <= $2::timestamptz order by created desc limit $3

select u.nickname, fullname, about, email from forums_users
join users u on forums_users.id = u.id
where forum = $1 order by u.nickname desc limit $2
select id, parent, message, isEdit, forum, created, thread, author from posts where thread = $1 order by rootParent, mPath limit $2
select nickname, fullname, about, email from users where nickname = $1

SELECT typinput=$2::regproc, typtype   FROM pg_catalog.pg_type   LEFT   JOIN (select ns.oid as nspoid, ns.nspname, r.r           from pg_namespace as ns           join ( select s.r, (current_schemas($3))[s.r] as nspname                    from generate_series($4, array_upper(current_schemas($5), $6)) as s(r) ) as r          using ( nspname )        ) as sp     ON sp.nspoid = typnamespace  WHERE typname = $1  ORDER BY sp.r, pg_type.oid DESC LIMIT $7

select id, parent, message, isEdit, forum, created, thread, author
			from posts where rootParent in
			(select id from posts where thread = $1 and parent = $4 and id < (select rootParent from posts where id = $2)  order by id desc limit $3) order by rootParent desc, mPath
select id from threads where id = $1
select id, parent, message, isEdit, forum, created, thread, author from posts where thread = $1 order by rootParent desc, mPath desc limit $2

select id, parent, message, isEdit, forum, created, thread, author
			from posts where rootParent in
			(select id from posts where thread = $1 and parent = $4 and id > (select rootParent from posts where id = $2)  order by id limit $3) order by rootParent, mPath
select id, parent, message, isEdit, forum, created, thread, author from posts where thread = $1 and mPath < (select mPath from posts where id = $2)  order by rootParent desc, mPath desc limit $3

select u.nickname, fullname, about, email from forums_users
join users u on forums_users.id = u.id
where forum = $1 and u.nickname < $2 order by u.nickname desc limit $3
SELECT n.nspname = ANY(current_schemas($2)), n.nspname, t.typname FROM pg_catalog.pg_type t JOIN pg_catalog.pg_namespace n ON t.typnamespace = n.oid WHERE t.oid = $1
select slug from forums where slug = $1
select id, parent, message, isEdit, forum, created, thread, author from posts where thread = $1 order by id desc limit $2
select slug, title, posts, threads, owner from forums where slug = $1
select current_database() as a, current_schemas($1) as b
select id, parent, message, isEdit, forum, created, thread, author from posts where thread = $1 and id < $2 order by id desc limit $3

select id, parent, message, isEdit, forum, created, thread, author
			from posts where rootParent in
			(select id from posts where thread = $1 and parent = $3 order by id desc limit $2) order by rootParent desc, mPath
commit
select id from threads where slug = $1

select u.nickname, fullname, about, email from forums_users
join users u on forums_users.id = u.id
where forum = $1 and u.nickname > $2 order by u.nickname limit $3

select id, parent, message, isEdit, forum, created, thread, author
			from posts where rootParent in
			(select id from posts where thread = $1 and parent = $3 order by id limit $2) order by rootParent, mPath
select id, parent, message, isEdit, forum, created, thread, author from posts where thread = $1 order by id limit $2
SELECT pg_stat_statements_reset()
begin
select id, title, message, votes, slug, created, forum, author from threads where forum = $1 order by created limit $2
select id, parent, message, isEdit, forum, created, thread, author from posts where id = $1
rollback
select id, parent, message, isEdit, forum, created, thread, author from posts where thread = $1 and mPath > (select mPath from posts where id = $2)  order by rootParent, mPath limit $3
select id, title, message, votes, slug, created, forum, author from threads where id = $1::bigint
select id, title, message, votes, slug, created, forum, author from threads where forum = $1 and created >= $2::timestamptz order by created limit $3
select id, title, message, votes, slug, created, forum, author from threads where forum = $1 order by created desc limit $2
select id, parent, message, isEdit, forum, created, thread, author from posts where thread = $1 and id > $2 order by id limit $3
select id, title, message, votes, slug, created, forum, author from threads where slug = $1
